{"tid":2194141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首長滿意度最後一名，柯臉色鐵青不給媒體問","createTime":"2020-09-08T10:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:12:21.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3eaf949723ea6ea697b600c010490cdabf935ae1","tid":2194141,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"《天下雜誌》今天公布首長滿意度調查，屏東縣長潘孟安、新北市長侯友宜以及桃園市長 鄭文燦，分別拿下前三名寶座，反觀台北市長柯文哲，從去年的倒數第二名掉到倒數第一 。柯下午出席後疫情論壇前被媒體追問此事，他臉色鐵青、不發一語，匆匆步入會場不願 表示意見。<br />\n<br />\n柯下午出席後疫情論壇前，被媒體包圍追問民調一事，但他全程不發一語，僅詢問一旁幕 僚要走哪邊，接著匆匆步入會場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akqBfZh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakqBfZh.png&h=d98bde00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/532TicD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F532TicD.jpg&h=15c64711&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceeiujj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fceeiujj.jpg&h=b5b03d57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ghFNnEj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FghFNnEj.png&h=d4a37e1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e61a4a9d4ffe89bac4cce6686b23ec1a05cce51a","tid":2194141,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"搞咩, 仲差過KMT <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad68e48ddddeceac4709028c56a41924b380ad3","tid":2194141,"uid":286897,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7b7e2731076d3f1a358b5b637370ec7652eb443","tid":2194141,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e61a4a9d4ffe89bac4cce6686b23ec1a05cce51a","tid":2194141,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"搞咩, 仲差過KMT <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09